.TH "nvme_subsystem_get_attr" 9 "nvme_subsystem_get_attr" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_subsystem_get_attr \- Read subsystem sysfs attribute
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "char *" nvme_subsystem_get_attr
.BI "(nvme_subsystem_t s "  ","
.BI "const char *attr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "s" 12
nvme_subsystem_t object
.IP "attr" 12
sysfs attribute name
.SH "RETURN"
String with the contents of \fIattr\fP or NULL in case of an empty
value or error.
